### Banking Transactions API - Sample Requests
### Use with REST Client extension in VS Code or similar tools
### Base URL: http://localhost:3000

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@transactionId = {{createTransaction.response.body.id}}
@accountId = ACC-12345

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### 1. Create a Transfer Transaction
# @name createTransaction
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "toAccount": "ACC-67890",
  "amount": 100.50,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "transfer"
}

### 2. Create a Deposit Transaction
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-99999",
  "toAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "amount": 500.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "deposit"
}

