### 5. Get All Transactions
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions

### 6. Get Transaction by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions/{{transactionId}}

### 7. Filter Transactions by Account
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions?accountId={{accountId}}

### 8. Filter Transactions by Type
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions?type=transfer

### 9. Filter Transactions by Date Range
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions?from=2024-01-01&to=2024-12-31

### 10. Combine Multiple Filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions?accountId={{accountId}}&type=transfer&from=2024-01-01&to=2024-12-31

### 11. Get Account Balance
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/{{accountId}}/balance

### 12. Get Account Summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/{{accountId}}/summary

### 13. Get Balance for Another Account
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/ACC-67890/balance

### 14. Get Summary for Another Account
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/ACC-67890/summary

### Error Cases - Invalid Account Format
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/INVALID-123/balance

### Error Cases - Invalid Transaction ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions/non-existent-id

